"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-rafael-nadal-to-skip-paris-olympic-singles-after-carlos-alcaraz-doubles-win-novak-djokovic\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999962389454382, \"rank\": 3.53182194551123e-06, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbRafael Nadal to skip Paris Olympic singles after Carlos Alcaraz doubles win?\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999962389454382, \"rank\": 3.53182194551123e-06, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1442941117637512e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rafael Nadal said that he does not know if he will play singles at the Paris Olympics after picking up a thigh injury in training.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rafael Nadalsaid on Saturday that he does not know if he will play singles at theParis Olympicsafter picking up a thigh injury in training.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  Nadal is due to face Hungary'sMarton Fucsovicsin the first round on Sunday and victory would hand him a 60th career clash with old rival NovakDjokovic.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9982057561072751, \"rank\": 0.0017974680897570247, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know what's going to happen, I do not know if I am going to play tomorrow or not,\\\" said the 38-year-old Spaniard, who is at his farewell Olympics and is also in the men's doubles.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.6319609301864971, \"rank\": 0.5821734886246708, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will talk to my people and make the smartest decision that I can to have the best chance of bringing a medal home, so let us see.\\\"\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, who has been plagued by injuries throughout his career, teamed up withCarlos Alcarazfor the first time and defeatedArgentina's Maximo Gonzalez and Andres Molteni 7-6 (7/4), 6-4 in front of a packed, raucous crowd under the roof on Court Philippe Chatrier.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, a singles gold medallist at the 2008 Beijing Olympics and doubles title winner at Rio four years later, appeared on court with a bandage strapped around his right thigh.\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997297848866012, \"rank\": 0.00027028814934472575, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is just his seventh tournament of 2024, in a season where he has also battled a hip injury and seen his singles ranking plummet to 161.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes more is not always more, sometimes more is less,\\\" added Nadal over the decision he faces.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just enjoying the moment playing doubles together with Carlos,\\\" added Nadal, who featured in the opening ceremony on Friday when he carried the Olympic torch.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been an unforgettable day for me today and an unforgettable day yesterday.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am enjoying every single moment, having the best experience possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hours earlier when Alcaraz had opened his singles campaign with a straights sets victory over Hady Habib, the 21-year-old said it was a \\\"dream\\\" to play alongside his compatriot Nadal.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2190, \"end\": 2197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9389263047718897e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2265, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hady Habib\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hady_Habib\"}, {\"begin\": 2348, \"end\": 2353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo appeared to a standing ovation on the same packed court where Nadal won 14 French Opens and Alcaraz collected his first just last month.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2439, \"end\": 2445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7259830609862654, \"rank\": 0.2641717545995949, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2456, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9389263047718897e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gonzalez and Molteni, the sixth seeds, entered the arena to a chorus of boos in the aftermath of a recent racism row between Argentina and France.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"score\": 0.9691477263411209, \"rank\": 0.031834438466386526, \"text\": \"Molteni\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\"}, {\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9835397048937662, \"rank\": 0.012650423617419238, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9950704291120838, \"rank\": 0.00495280797935987, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spanish pair endured a nightmare start when Alcaraz was broken in the first game.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9921231464296519, \"rank\": 0.006475582857479428, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9389263047718897e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having not played doubles on tour since 2022, the rustiness was not surprising.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The greater experience of Nadal was key and the break was quickly retrieved with the veteran's reflexes as razor sharp as ever at the net.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2843, \"end\": 2848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz and Nadal went to three set points in the tiebreaker and a pinpoint backhand down the line by Nadal secured the opener.\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9389263047718897e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 2969, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 3059, \"end\": 3064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.29257407608795e-22, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gonzalez and Molteni raced to a 3-0 lead in the second set but back came the Spanish pair to level.\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"score\": 0.9691477263411209, \"rank\": 0.031834438466386526, \"text\": \"Molteni\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molteni\"}, {\"begin\": 3163, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9921231464296519, \"rank\": 0.006475582857479428, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rafael Nadal secured another key break with a rasping backhand return to allow him and his partner to lead 5-4 and the opportunity to serve for the match.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3187, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That honour fell to the 22-time Grand Slam title champion and victory was secured when Alcaraz slapped the winning forehand crouching at the net.\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3430, \"end\": 3437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9389263047718897e-22, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garrin Lambley \\u00a9 Agence France-Presse  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.9928538387618631, \"rank\": 0.007197596417537056, \"text\": \"Lambley\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\"}, {\"begin\": 3510, \"end\": 3530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 3532, \"end\": 3535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.8615329043393032, \"rank\": 0.160721767509